1.create project - ng new project-name

2.to run angular project - ng serve

3.to generate component - ng g c component-name


basic concepts 

1. Module : To import libraries ( Root Module- App Module )

2. Components : To generate ts,html,css, Root component-App component

3. Data Binding - sharing data within a component

    3.1 One way Binding - only single directional sharing

        3.1.1 component (ts file) to View (html page)

             3.1.1.1 String Interpolation - {{variable-name}}
             3.1.1.2 Property Binding - [tag attribute] = "class-property"

        3.1.2 View to Component
          
             3.1.2.1 Event Binding - [event name]= "function- call"
             3.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - [event name]= "function- call ($event)"
             3.1.2.3 Template Referencing variable - syntax : #variable-name

     3.2 Two way Binding - same time data sharing in both direction

        3.2.1 FormsModule - import in Appmodule
          ngModel - syntax : [(ngModel)]="variable name" set name attribute if its in a form tag

4. Component path set up  -router-outlet selector

5. Dependency Injection - inside constructor

6. angular service

7. ngSubmit

8. Angular form

     8.1 Template Driven Forms

     8.2 Model Driven Forms - ReactivrForms - Import ReactivrFormsModule
          (form group,form array,form control)

9. Angular Directives - DOM Manipulation

     9.1 Component Directives

     9.2 Structural Directives - prefix *

          9.2.1 *ngIf
          9.2.2 *ngFor

     9.3 Attribute Directives

10. Parent Child Communication

     10.1 parent-child - @Input
     10.2 child- parent -@OUtpit()